text.textblock: Meeting of the National Advisory Council for Health Care Policy, Research, and Evaluation

usdept.textblock: DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES

usbureau.textblock: Agency for Health Care Policy and Research

agency.textblock: Agency for Health Care Policy and Research.

action.textblock: Change in the notice of public meeting.

summary.textblock: The meeting of the National Advisory Council for Health
Care Policy, Research, and Evaluation will not be held in Washington, D.C. as published in the
of December 27, 1993, vol. 58, no. 246, page 68418. The primary speakers for the open portion of the meeting are unable to attend due to scheduling conflicts.

date.textblock: The open meeting was scheduled for Monday, January 24,
1994, from 9 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. A closed portion of the meeting to review grant applications will be conducted through a telephone conference call on Tuesday, January 25, 1994, 12 noon.

further.textblock: Deborah L. Queenan, Executive Secretary of the Advisory Council at the Agency for Health Care Policy and Research, 2101 East Jefferson Street, suite 603, Rockville, Maryland 20852, (301) 594-1459.
